Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so I tell atheists\Ndon't bother
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't work for you\Nbecause it is divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the source of truth\Nso if you deny divinity
