Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fruits, the benefits of knowing truth\Nfrom falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:23:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so when we say glory and\Nexcelsis Deo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we signify that God\Nis sovereign
