Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so the road to salvation\Nis
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,traverses the road\Nthe road of salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the road of truth\Nthe road of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to salvation\Nthe road of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:24:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to salvation\Nalright
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the test differentiates\Nessence from appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because truth has to do with essence\Nand truth has to do with appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and appearance can fool anyone, anybody\Nbecause truth comes from the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.86,0:24:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and falsehood can deceive many people\Nnow we have the slide honey
