Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.08,0:24:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's so critical\NI want to show that right up in front
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:24:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,now this is what the world does not know\Nthis is what the world does not know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.92,0:25:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what the world does not know\Nhere it says
