Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.86,0:25:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,vote for me\Nand don't pay any attention
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.22,0:25:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to that one there\Nand that's what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,every day on television\Nwhat you see every day on television
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.79,0:25:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the government's collapsing\Nthe corporations are collapsing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.16,0:25:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the corporations are collapsing\Nwhole industries are collapsing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.69,0:25:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,how can that be\Nthat's how it can be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the president of the company\Nand I will make you all rich
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.96,0:26:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as I have helped myself\NI'm the president of the company
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.00,0:26:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will make you all rich as soon as I have helped myself\Nso you can see you need a sense of humor
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so we go back to the beginning of the slides\Nthe way we had them set up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so we discovered this whole system\Nby accident
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.58,0:26:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,actually I discovered it by accident\Nby accident
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I forget now how I discovered it\Noh yes I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.42,0:27:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I attended a lecture on kinesiology\Nand I was showing the staff of my clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,how to use it\NI was in an exercise class
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.26,0:27:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was showing to my students\Nhow to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.99,0:27:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was showing to my students\Nhow to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.65,0:27:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to our hospital staff to show how this works.\NWhen people look at fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,just looking at the light makes their arm weak.\NSo I was demonstrating this to the staff of the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.27,0:28:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted a couple of volunteers.\NSo I said, we had a group that was working on the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.81,0:28:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They were trying to cure various diseases at the clinic.\NAnd some of their students on the Course in Miracles were standing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.14,0:28:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, come along with me, I just want to show something.\NAnd I took a couple of the students with me to do this test in front of my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.66,0:28:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited a few students.\NI invited a few students who were doing miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.66,0:28:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said to the students, now look at this fluorescent light.\NSo they looked at the fluorescent light like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.51,0:29:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I pressed down on their arm, and they did not go weak.\NI said, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.42,0:29:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And they said, what is this?\NAnd I said, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.42,0:29:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?\NAll these other people, their arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.42,0:29:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But these people, their arm does not go weak.\NSo then I found that spiritual orientation changes your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.95,0:29:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual person does not go weak when they look at fluorescent lights.\NA spiritual person does not go weak when they look at fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.04,0:30:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, wow, wow.\NSpiritual orientation changes your physical response to stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.80,0:30:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual orientation changes your physical response to stimuli.\NSpiritual orientation changes your whole energy balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.60,0:30:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual orientation changes your energy balance.\NSo to do the research further,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.66,0:30:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some students who were starting the Course of Miracles.\NStudents.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.29,0:30:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had five or six. I forget.\NAnd I tested them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.98,0:30:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They looked at the fluorescent light\Nand they all went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.79,0:31:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just starting the Course in Miracles.\NSo then, you know, the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.48,0:31:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is a spiritual lesson, a new one every day\Nfor a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.07,0:31:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I retested them.\NI retested them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.56,0:31:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, oh, every week or two.\NI retested this group of students
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.72,0:31:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who were starting the Course in Miracles\Nevery week or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.46,0:31:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the new students\Nalways went weak to the fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.30,0:31:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tested them.\NI tested them every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And every week, they went weak.\NThey went, every week, they went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.15,0:32:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, around Lesson 70,\Nabout the 70th day of a Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.47,0:32:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lesson 70, about the 70th day,\Nthey no longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.23,0:32:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they no longer went weak with the fluorescent light.\NThey were immune to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.91,0:32:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They would look at the light\Nand their arm would stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a major discovery.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.95,0:32:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried it at home and proved it too.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.41,0:32:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that led to the research\Nand calibrating myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the levels of consciousness.\NAnd it led eventually to the map that you see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.59,0:33:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're born at one particular level of consciousness.\NHaving to do with past karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.50,0:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's true.\NThe level of consciousness at birth
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.10,0:33:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,reflects one's past karma.\NSo, it's not accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.25,0:33:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not accidental.\NEverything is by design.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.39,0:33:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The design is intrinsic\Nto the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.71,0:34:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Nwhat we began researching then
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.01,0:34:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,was the field of consciousness itself.\NSo, we started to study the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.59,0:34:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that arose the scale.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.51,0:34:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been verified over and over again,\Nover decades now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.03,0:34:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Over decades.\NIt seems very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very reliable.\NIt seems very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.86,0:34:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very reliable.\NAnd it's useful as a research tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.51,0:34:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's useful as a research tool.\NThis is very accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.59,0:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very useful as a research tool.\NSo, it's a clinical fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.86,0:34:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a clinical fact.\NNow, the theory of why it works
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.07,0:34:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is variable.\NAnd it's really not understandable
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.13,0:35:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get to the field of quantum mechanics.\NAdvanced theoretical physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.82,0:35:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really not understandable until you get to the field of quantum mechanics.\NYes.
