Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.36,0:36:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I'm holding in mind affects her response,\Nand she doesn't even know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.51,0:36:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't know what I'm thinking in my head,\Nwhat I'm thinking in my head is,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.01,0:36:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is affected by sugar.\NIt's also directly connected to Susan's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.03,0:36:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're addressing the infinite field of consciousness itself,\Nand we need to say something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.15,0:37:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of consciousness has no beginning and no end.\NIt is outside of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.59,0:37:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet includes all of time.\NThisクール formidable
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.01,0:37:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is outside of time,\Nwhile it includes all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.67,0:37:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is outside of time,\NBecause the field of energy, because the field of energy of consciousness, the energy, has no beginning or no end. It has no middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.73,0:38:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is infinite has no beginning, no end, and no middle.\NAs you can see with a little reflection, that which is infinite, there is no here or there, there is no now or then, there is no past or future.
