Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.40,0:39:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is no cause\Nnothing is caused
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.11,0:39:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no cause\Nif there is no cause
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.51,0:39:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,how does anything come to be\Nif nothing is caused
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.55,0:40:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then how do we\Nhow do we explain
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.42,0:40:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomena of life\Nif nothing is caused
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.03,0:40:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,then how do we explain\Nthe phenomena of life
